            <title>[LU-1756] compat code clean up</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1756</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Clean up compat so that:&lt;br/&gt;
1. unused macros/functions are removed&lt;br/&gt;
2. redundant definitions are removed&lt;br/&gt;
3. client/server common functions are moved to lustre_common.h which is not compat code&lt;br/&gt;
4. use latest kernel functions and define functions for older kernel as wrappers to latest kernel APIs.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
